# =============================================================================
# Amprenta RAG Platform - Environment Configuration Template
# =============================================================================
#
# WORKSTATION SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#
# First Time Setup on ANY Workstation:
#   1. git clone https://github.com/BardGeesaman/Notion_RAG.git
#   2. cd Notion_RAG
#   3. bash scripts/setup_workstation.sh
#      (This automatically copies this template to .env and sets YOUR_USERNAME_HERE)
